dct_description_sm: Relief shown pictorially and by spot heights.
Also shows portions of Uganda, Sudan, Ethiopia, Somali Republic, and Tanzania.
Includes distance table, location map, text, and col. ill.
Inset maps of Nairobi and Mombasa, tourist information, list of animal species found, charts of climatic conditions, text, and col. ill. on verso.
